<li>Seraphilm (male, late 20s, able to do standard American, midwest American, and southern American accents. Nothing international, though, unless you want unintentional racism)</li>
<li>Yakovlev (Male, early 20s, able to do standard American, southern American, and Russian)</li>
<li>Shotgun Saint (Male, early 20s, able to do standard American and a small variety of British accents)</li>
<li>AllyReggie (Female, mid 20s, able to do most of the 21 accent tour with varying authenticity - ask for more info)</li>
</ul>
