<li><strong>Status:</strong> Script written and peer reviewed, need audio.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>&quot;Work Title Two: The Sequel&quot; <em>(hyperlinked to sandbox)</em>
<ul>
<li style="list-style: none; display: inline">
<ul>
<li>Roles for 4 men</li>
<li>In need of sound engineer</li>
<li><strong>Status:</strong> Audio recorded, needs to be edited together</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Col. Hornby</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><em>You wake up in a padded cell&#8230;</em> text/audio multimedia project; possibly eventual framework for CYOA story. Still at drawing board stage.</li>
</ul>
</div>
